_sText:
Hello everyone!

I want to present for you my new Trikz_Lucky map.

This map is not for the newcomers, but for the experienced Trikz players.

This map consist of 11 levels, starting by medium difficulty and ending by hard difficulty.

The map is made in gray tones, with the addition of custom textures. [Dev Texture]

In the end, you will find some music and a small bonus.

I really hope that you will enjoy playing on my map!

Separately, I want to express special thanks to all the players who helped me!
